The 'agent': refers to the Python/Langgraph AI Agent whose main file structure is at /src/agent

The 'frontend': refers to the Angular/TypeScript/Node app at /web, that runs at localhost:4200

The 'database': the spreadsheet at /data/agent_research.xslx' generated by the agent.

The 'run file': the timestamped file (e.g. (Run_2026-05-06_21-25-11_AEST.md) showing the searches done, the resurces, gathered, etc. generated in /data after each run.

'screenshot 1' (or something similar) refers to '1.png' in the '/docs/screenshots' folder